Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.40,0:00:20.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事隔八年看见哥哥的面容
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.46,0:00:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是杀人者的嘴脸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.24,0:00:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕我也是同样的嘴脸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.08,0:00:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前的Freyja真的是你发射的?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.66,0:00:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 原本打算阻止哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.39,0:00:39.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便杀死哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.97,0:00:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不能把Freyja 把这Damocles的钥匙交给哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.28,0:00:47.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算被哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.95,0:00:49.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用了GEASS
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.41,0:00:53.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对娜娜莉使用GEASS?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.24,0:00:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我期望过无数次
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.12,0:01:01.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕只让娜娜莉重见光明
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.94,0:01:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 王者的力量 绝对服从的GEASS也无法对娜娜莉使用
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.03,0:01:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那现在呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.23,0:01:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.15,0:01:15.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果再扭曲娜娜莉的意志 我就是…



Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.50,0:02:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,RE;


Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.91,0:03:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡莲 无论如何都要阻挠吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.75,0:03:03.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀 我误会了你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.39,0:03:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本以为作法不同 你也在以你的方式为日本着想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.40,0:03:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.40,0:03:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和鲁鲁修有必须完成的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.66,0:03:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 这么想要力量吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.11,0:03:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.22,0:03:20.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.25,0:03:23.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不该留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.37,0:03:25.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,击败你 阻止鲁鲁修
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.95,0:03:27.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会让你如愿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.63,0:03:41.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利瓦尔不去逃难吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.22,0:03:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要逃去哪?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.02,0:03:45.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这倒也是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.59,0:03:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能和大家每天过得开心就满足了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.06,0:03:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.04,0:03:57.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有主君的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.99,0:03:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是依靠着谁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.90,0:04:00.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脆弱的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.68,0:04:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别去 您这伤…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.23,0:04:13.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须为起始的责任负责
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.43,0:04:15.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为领导者的资格
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.90,0:04:19.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥没有掌握这个世界的资格
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.76,0:04:23.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自称ZERO践踏人意志的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.78,0:04:28.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就该继续逃亡生活吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.18,0:04:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要终日为逃避暗杀而奔波的未来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.69,0:04:33.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了你的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.37,0:04:36.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么时候恳求过那种事?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.07,0:04:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只要和哥哥在一起生活就足够
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.25,0:04:44.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 现实被各种因素所支配
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.51,0:04:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抗争是必不可少的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.30,0:04:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为此 才作为反抗组织战斗至今
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.31,0:04:52.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理应也有组织中实现的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.73,0:04:58.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些无法加入组织和系统的人该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.81,0:05:02.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在怎么能断言这是错的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.94,0:05:04.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.65,0:05:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别居高临下教训人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.56,0:05:11.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能进入组织的人该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.69,0:05:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓正义…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.87,0:05:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果服从侵略者的做法 就等于承认他们的行为
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.00,0:05:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是现在出击会死
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.69,0:05:23.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就算这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.43,0:05:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.71,0:05:32.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只懂得这种活法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.32,0:05:36.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤堂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.74,0:05:39.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要争斗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.83,0:05:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要还有必须保护之人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.97,0:06:00.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许失去了对战争应有的矜持与美学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.44,0:06:04.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便这样也必须有容身处
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.78,0:06:07.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只为此战斗到现在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.65,0:06:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直人 我们这样做对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.47,0:06:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但人称战争是发明之母
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.20,0:06:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不承认
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.53,0:06:21.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布丁伯爵没有看到人在其中的作用
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.26,0:06:22.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是叫妮娜来着?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.88,0:06:24.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么说?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.11,0:06:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是尽自己所能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.58,0:06:29.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想重蹈覆辙而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.33,0:06:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但人是脆弱的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.20,0:06:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 有梦想错了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.70,0:06:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道我连这资格都没吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.47,0:06:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明还能干下去 能干下去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.94,0:06:44.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么大家都看不起我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.52,0:06:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.84,0:06:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看见了 看到现在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.46,0:06:53.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抗争就是人类的历史
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.17,0:06:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.97,0:06:58.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人和世界是如此难以如人所愿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.02,0:07:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你就想人家都听你的?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.88,0:07:01.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.48,0:07:03.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是卑劣的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.48,0:07:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扭曲人心 践踏人尊严的GEASS
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.78,0:07:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那Damocles又如何
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.18,0:07:13.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强制令人俯首称臣的系统 就不卑劣吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.59,0:07:17.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Damocles会成为仇恨的象征
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.54,0:07:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仇恨会汇集于此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.61,0:07:23.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了让大家能迎接明天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.64,0:07:28.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 娜娜莉你也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.82,0:07:29.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.04,0:07:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁鲁修．V．布里塔尼亚下令
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.01,0:07:35.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把Damocles的钥匙给我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.43,0:07:48.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.57,0:07:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能交给哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.25,0:07:55.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能再 罪上加罪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.74,0:08:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请吧 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.94,0:08:07.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耍小聪明



