Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.51,0:08:17.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆散
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.47,0:08:21.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纪录下来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.92,0:08:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰雷米亚．哥特瓦尔德
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.50,0:08:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带给你败北的 有纪念意义的男人之名
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.77,0:08:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纪念? 那和我无关
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.57,0:08:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我没有记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.41,0:08:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记忆?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.12,0:08:38.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.87,0:08:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动起来 Tristan
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.85,0:08:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕只能飞也好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.70,0:08:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下辐射波动也用尽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.59,0:08:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,护盾能量也耗完了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.47,0:08:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.91,0:09:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赢不了?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.36,0:09:07.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连GEASS的诅咒都用上了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.57,0:09:09.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡莲 如此强大
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.64,0:09:11.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是这边的规格比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.12,0:09:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀 有这样的力量 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.87,0:09:22.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结束吧 卡莲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.37,0:09:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你如果有正义的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.18,0:09:41.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会 没打到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.22,0:09:44.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 你打到了 卡莲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.49,0:10:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 你赢了 卡莲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.62,0:10:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.26,0:10:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经在靠自己的意志活着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.85,0:10:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我也能走自己的路
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.01,0:10:25.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.51,0:10:28.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爱你 娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.66,0:10:37.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你用了吧 GEASS
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.13,0:10:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.70,0:10:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 站住
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.22,0:10:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥是恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.75,0:11:01.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卑劣 无耻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.36,0:11:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…太过分
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.42,0:11:12.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背叛者枢木朱雀已败
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.07,0:11:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你无意求生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.58,0:11:15.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了那位大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.94,0:11:20.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神乐耶 你最近才得知鲁鲁修的真面目
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.59,0:11:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这又如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.74,0:11:25.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但却理解他的一部分本质
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.26,0:11:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.47,0:11:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通告全世界
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.41,0:11:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是神圣布里塔尼亚帝国皇帝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.19,0:11:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁鲁修．V．布里塔尼亚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.14,0:11:48.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能 鲁鲁修使用了Freyja代表…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.77,0:11:49.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.90,0:11:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.34,0:11:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修奈泽尔已加入我麾下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.54,0:11:59.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至此 Damocles与Freyja也全部为我所用
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.24,0:12:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑骑士团不再拥有与我对抗的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.58,0:12:08.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样也要垂死挣扎的话 招待你们的只会是Freyja
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.47,0:12:13.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经无人能阻我霸业
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.01,0:12:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 今天这一瞬间 世界已陷落我手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.31,0:12:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁鲁修．V．布里塔尼亚下令
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.34,0:12:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界啊 臣服于我吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.47,0:12:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All Hail Lelouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.52,0:12:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All Hail Lelouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.74,0:12:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All Hail Lelouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.75,0:12:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All Hail Lelouch!




Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.18,0:12:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神圣布里塔尼亚帝国第99代唯一皇帝陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.60,0:12:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兼黑骑士团C.E.O. 超合众国第2代最高评议会议长

Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.05,0:13:02.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁鲁修．V．布里塔尼亚陛下出现在我们眼前



Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.79,0:13:05.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.61,0:13:10.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反对鲁鲁修陛下的愚昧之徒 正被送往刑场
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.42,0:13:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次大战中 帝都Pendragon和众多将士
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.60,0:13:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包括Knight of Zero枢木朱雀卿在内 付出了惨重的牺牲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.97,0:13:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,E.U.批准超合众国宪章
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.45,0:13:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的鲁鲁修陛下 终于实现了世界统一伟业
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.78,0:13:31.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光荣与鲁鲁修陛下同在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.95,0:13:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All Hail Britannia!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.78,0:13:35.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All Hail Lelouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.85,0:13:37.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么光荣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.46,0:13:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,单纯的独裁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.80,0:13:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反抗者全部被杀死
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.84,0:13:44.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘘 被人听到的话会满门抄斩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.85,0:13:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然不得不把这种内容作为正义报导
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.58,0:13:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁鲁修 这就是你想做的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.65,0:13:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,支配世界和人们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.99,0:13:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们也真傻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.30,0:14:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时何必与鲁鲁修顶嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.95,0:14:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为迎来明天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.61,0:14:07.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算重复着成功与失败也必须前行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.48,0:14:10.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人和科学是一样的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.48,0:14:12.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是进化
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.06,0:14:14.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是进步 布丁伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.52,0:14:16.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个称呼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.94,0:14:18.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还在记恨吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.69,0:14:20.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你猜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.86,0:14:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗伊德先生和拉克夏塔以前发生过什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.48,0:14:28.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是些琐碎的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.80,0:14:31.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在想想根本不算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.95,0:14:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出发点而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.48,0:14:44.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.62,0:14:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在出去正中他们下怀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.38,0:14:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.44,0:14:53.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.10,0:15:03.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.92,0:15:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.39,0:15:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.10,0:15:08.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人 鲁鲁修在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.58,0:15:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道鲁鲁修他们策划的是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.08,0:15:29.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开枪 我来对付他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.98,0:15:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧 假面骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.68,0:15:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.65,0:15:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀 按约定你来杀死我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.00,0:15:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何都要做吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.54,0:16:00.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按预定 世界的仇很正集中在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.87,0:16:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我消失 就能斩断这仇恨的锁链
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.87,0:16:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑骑士团留有ZERO的传说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.83,0:16:12.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修奈泽尔也会听命于ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.48,0:16:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样世界将不再用军事力量 而是在谈判桌上就能解决
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.59,0:16:21.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能朝明天前进
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.36,0:16:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.61,0:16:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,零之镇魂曲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.95,0:16:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在C的世界中 我们明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.03,0:16:40.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人们期望着明天
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.81,0:16:43.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.29,0:16:45.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不觉得愿望和GEASS很像吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.36,0:16:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠自己无法实现的事会寻求他人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.58,0:16:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿望吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.30,0:17:00.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就对所有人使用名为愿望的GEASS


Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.17,0:17:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了世界的明天
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.43,0:17:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁鲁修 你作为对人使用GEASS的代价
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.18,0:17:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有被杀的觉悟 才有资格开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.76,0:17:29.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀 你要成为英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.46,0:17:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从世界的敌人

Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.40,0:17:34.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇帝鲁鲁修．V．布里塔尼亚手中拯救世界的救世主



Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.67,0:17:36.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.14,0:17:49.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁…鲁鲁修
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.77,0:17:52.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这对你来说也是惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.21,0:18:01.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你必须作为正义的使者戴着面具活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.44,0:18:06.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不再是枢木朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.35,0:18:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也必须为世界牺牲常人该有的幸福 永远
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.32,0:18:18.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这份GEASS 我确实收到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.66,0:18:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.11,0:18:56.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…哥哥之前都是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.37,0:19:01.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 我爱你

Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.94,0:19:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…毁灭世界…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.00,0:19:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,创造…世界…



Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.01,0:19:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.15,0:19:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睁开眼睛 哥哥 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.49,0:19:33.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔王鲁鲁修已死
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.75,0:19:35.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,释放人质
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.00,0:19:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好 撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.30,0:19:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂且撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.34,0:19:47.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道那是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.45,0:19:48.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.63,0:19:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是 ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.43,0:19:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耍赖 我有哥哥就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.14,0:20:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有哥哥的明天…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.29,0:20:51.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁鲁修
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.33,0:20:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之后世界好了不少
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.86,0:21:01.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用在战争上的能源 现在用在饥饿与贫困
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.31,0:21:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各种仇恨与罪名都被被你一手包办了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.76,0:21:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家比起Damocles这个系统 更容易记住一个有名有姓的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.62,0:21:18.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真够可笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.35,0:21:26.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 正因为如此 大家才不会被过去束缚 能继续前进
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.82,0:21:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又会笑着说“如我所料”了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.88,0:21:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然还留下了各种问题
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.16,0:21:37.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.18,0:22:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名为GEASS的王的力量 会令人孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.29,0:22:19.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是好像不太对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.82,0:22:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 鲁鲁修